可以用前 <span class="token number">3</span> 朵盛开的花制作第一束花。但不能使用后 <span class="token number">3</span> 朵盛开的花，因为它们不相邻。
<span class="token number">12</span> 天后：<span class="token punctuation">[</span>x<span class="token punctuation">,</span> x<span class="token punctuation">,</span> x<span class="token punctuation">,</span> x<span class="token punctuation">,</span> x<span class="token punctuation">,</span> x<span class="token punctuation">,</span> x<span class="token punctuation">]</span>
显然，我们可以用不同的方式制作两束花。
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>示例 4：</strong></p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code>输入：bloomDay <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1000000000</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">1000000000</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> m <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> k <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">1</span>
输出：<span class="token number">1000000000</span>
