</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>示例 2：</strong></p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code>输入：s1<span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">"ab"</span> s2 <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">"eidboaoo"</span>
